<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #9c78c1 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        header {
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            padding-top: 40px;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        header p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .content {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .section h2 {
            color: #3B82F6;
            font-size: 1.8em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #3B82F6;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .section p {
            color: #555;
            line-height: 1.8;
            font-size: 1.05em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2);
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: #3B82F6;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .team {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .team-member {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .team-member h3 {
            color: #3B82F6;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
        }

        .team-member p {
            color: #999;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        .cta-section h2 {
            color: white;
            border-bottom: 3px solid white;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 20px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .back-link::before {
            content: "← ";
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <a href="/" class="back-link">Back to Home</a>

        <header>
            <h1>About QueuePro</h1>
            <p>Smart Queue Management System for Modern Businesses</p>
        </header>

        <div class="content">
            <!-- Vision & Mission Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Our Vision & Mission</h2>
                <p>
                    QueuePro is designed to revolutionize how businesses manage customer queues and waiting times.
                    Our mission is to eliminate inefficiencies in queue management while improving customer satisfaction
                    and reducing operational costs.
                </p>
                <p>
                    We believe that smart queue management should be accessible to every business, regardless of size.
                    QueuePro empowers organizations to serve their customers better through intelligent queue
                    optimization
                    and real-time analytics.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Key Features Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <div class="features">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>📊 Analytics Dashboard</h3>
                        <p>Real-time insights into queue performance, peak hours, and customer wait times with detailed
                            reporting.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>👥 Smart Queue Management</h3>
                        <p>Intelligent routing and prioritization of customers ensure efficient service delivery and
                            minimal wait times.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>🔐 Secure Authentication</h3>
                        <p>Role-based access control with secure login systems for Citizens, Officers, and
                            Administrators.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>📱 Digital Token System</h3>
                        <p>Customers can generate and manage digital tokens for seamless queue entry without physical
                            documentation.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>⚡ Real-time Updates</h3>
                        <p>Live notifications and updates keep customers informed about their position and wait status.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>📋 Activity Logging</h3>
                        <p>Comprehensive logging of all activities for auditing, compliance, and performance analysis
                            purposes.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- How It Works Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p><strong>For Customers:</strong></p>
                <p>
                    Register on QueuePro and generate a digital token. No more waiting in crowded queues or losing your
                    spot.
                    Receive real-time updates about your position and estimated service time.
                </p>
                <p><strong>For Officers:</strong></p>
                <p>
                    Officers manage the queue efficiently through the dashboard, processing customers in optimal order
                    and accessing complete customer information at a glance.
                </p>
                <p><strong>For Administrators:</strong></p>
                <p>
                    Full system control with comprehensive analytics, user management, and business intelligence tools
                    to optimize operations.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Values Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Our Core Values</h2>
                <div class="features">
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Customer-Centric</h3>
                        <p>Every feature is designed with customers in mind, ensuring positive experiences.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Innovation</h3>
                        <p>Continuous improvement and adoption of latest technologies to stay ahead.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Reliability</h3>
                        <p>Dependable systems that businesses can trust for critical operations.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-card">
                        <h3>Transparency</h3>
                        <p>Clear communication and honest representation in all dealings.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Team Section -->
            <div class="section">
                <h2>Our Team</h2>
                <p>QueuePro is built by skilled professionals passionate about solving real-world problems.</p>
                <div class="team">
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <h3>Development Team</h3>
                        <p>Expert developers crafting robust solutions</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <h3>Design Team</h3>
                        <p>Creating intuitive and beautiful interfaces</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="team-member">
                        <h3>Support Team</h3>
                        <p>Always ready to help and support</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- CTA Section -->
            <div class="cta-section">
                <h2>Ready to Experience QueuePro?</h2>
                <p>Join thousands of businesses simplifying their queue management today.</p>
                <a href="/login" class="cta-button">Get Started</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>